Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,フワ・フワ・フユウして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:49.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キラめく遠くの空と ひとつになる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:58.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風読み気ままな わたしのゆくえは彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に行こう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:07.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸はずんでく世界の Spring Breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽にあつまるのみんなの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:20.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オハヨウとサヨナラの間はわたし達だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:23.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんでもできるね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:29.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透き通る日差し 生まれたての空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:36.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待ち合わせた 約束のMorning Arch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:43.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を振るキミへと とっておきの今日を渡そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.88,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}お喋りが始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.90,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘飘忽忽 浮游空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:49.71,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融身明媚广袤的晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:58.30,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心乘风 伴我行至远方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:01.62,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:07.34,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在春风中深呼吸着世界的 Spring Breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:13.34,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面带笑容的伙伴 聚集在太阳之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:20.09,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行走在早安与再见之间的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:23.84,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:29.98,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿透黑暗的日光 与之俱来的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:36.02,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们许下的 约定的Morning Arch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:43.40,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向挥手致意的你 献上美好的一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.88,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}永不止境的聊天要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:54.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}茜に並ぶ背高かげぼうし　たのしい一日のおわり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:03.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尽きないお喋り　まだまだあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:10.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そろそろおうちに帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:17.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}じゃあね　明日ね　メールするから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:25.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日のページにみんな　おそろいの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:32.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}じゃあね　明日ね　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:40.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日も一緒にいれて　ヨカッタな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:47.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風とココロ　ハミングする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:54.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}つぎの角で振り向きながら　バイバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:54.52,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}茜色影子 愉快的一天就此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:03.04,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然我们还有说不完的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:10.23,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是时候要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:17.65,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天见 我会发邮件的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:25.01,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在今天的一页印下我们一齐的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:32.21,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天见 感谢你们的陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:40.53,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也能和你们在一起很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:47.83,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}清风与心灵的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:54.44,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在下一个拐角 挥手道别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦 快一点 小透等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:01.03,TITLE,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\frz355.758\pos(410,628)}雨天就要泡澡{\fs40}-也像雨一样-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 昨天晚饭后我发过短信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？没看到这样的短信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！另一只忘穿了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话还不如光脚算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内...内...内...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说竟然会没意识到 竟然会没意识到...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能蹲下啊 能从前面看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为睡得太死了？ 就因为这点理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事 该怎么办啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 谁都有忘东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然忘穿内裤却是天下一绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 刚才...刚才...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想忘穿内裤是天下一绝对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦！不能跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透 你也够累的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 就是只有早晨比较迷糊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会睡着了 发呆了之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是啊 只是觉得万一的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 伦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午的课的笔记 能借我抄一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你昨天早退来的是吧 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么语？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 日语啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课的时候被睡魔袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是早晨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些潦草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有看不懂的地方的话要跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子 等下也给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 抄完了就给伦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 凪你近视吗？ 视力大约多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2.0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是平光镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要戴平光镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戴这个的话 不该看的东西也会看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在就在优子背后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 这是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说是开玩笑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是好骗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是普通的近视而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦 我最怕恐怖故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪的演技好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能进演剧部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经进了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是幽灵部员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这个夏天从你那收到两三次信了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着"想在东京得到相当的地位 拜托你了"的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是第二封信来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:11.03,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}（摘自夏目漱石代表作之一 「心」的“下 先生与遗书”第一段）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}下一章的“老师”→文章中的“我”\N理清个人主义思想和其伦理观之间的一条界限\N请思考从“老师”的信中能读出来的人间的自我和葛藤的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 "想去厕所"太难为情了说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我头好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子 那是肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不对 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去厕所 带优子去保健室的时候 顺带去一下可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 伦 真的帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 伦也去厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦！伦 怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚 就是很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是中什么邪了 好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所吗 还是去保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 厕所 厕...to...to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 找小透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦 伦 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子 在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦 一下子失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保健室老师也不在 该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点啊 比如联络别的老师什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:26.96,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 早上还是晴天来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是小雨 用跑的应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我发觉了 其实我是雨女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}（雨女 日本民间传说中的呼唤风雨的妖怪）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用死撑了 快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊 死盯着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在小伦偏偏还是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦 我们去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我选这学校太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.24,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,合宿参加承诺书请交至各负责老师或山田处。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦 得快点擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 穿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.69,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,锵~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.69,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（垃圾袋）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不需要伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:10:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这年龄了还穿这个太牵强了吧 小学生就另当别论
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 确实...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣装太牵强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其中一个人穿就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 重点不在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我脱掉好了反正我已经淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啥呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小凪和优子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我还在想你们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦你都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近 要不要来先把衣服弄干了再走？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？ 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但外头还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道校内有雨女不成？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是豪雨 跑过去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起遭殃就不怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 要是到小凪家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懊糟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被淋所以还是叫出租车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪是高中生该干的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一段时间会不会晴起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还是叫出租车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪家是往这边走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别落下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天明明会让心情忧郁 但她们依旧那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有灵感了 有灵感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:47.03,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\pos(246,166)}鬼头老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.03,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(184,168)}兴趣·诗歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.82,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(154,394)}诗歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.03,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1114,406)}现实
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去洗澡吧 洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？兄贵回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 你还有哥哥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我的朋友们刚刚来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间 不要去用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪喊你的哥哥叫兄贵的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫兄贵的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 因为浴室一次只能进去两人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要分成二组哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我和小伦先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 那么我们换身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 仔细想想我还没有和小透两人单独说过话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候的沉默有点 有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们放点什么东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DVD 有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真实存在的恐怖都市传说」和保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么把衣服放在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快点进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 是伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是放下了刘海 改变还真大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种反应 早就腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得要趁早洗完才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢 不快点跟小透和优子酱交换的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的房间里只有她们两人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 两人可是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽说是那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 把眼睛闭上就不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想叫出声来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点去洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 优子 浴室空了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？优子 糟了优子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～真是吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以洗澡了 是吧 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 透在洗头发时有没有因为看不到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而感到害怕的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候非常受不了洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 洗发水进眼里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋浴在什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛 眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说优子 太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我都以为快要断气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 意识变得朦胧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦 快看啊 看到绿洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子　水的温度怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 把暖气关掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算是要弄干衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多干了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨快点停下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还是不行的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天的时候就要说到梳理头发了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头发总是黏在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头发会叉开来完全整理不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因为发质不一样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优的头发让我摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 优子的头发真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有分叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐这个衣服很可爱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 现在正是最关键的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要刷新凪的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子的指甲真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有做过什么保养吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很舒服 总觉得很让人好害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 要我怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨好像还没停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下得真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是我很喜欢雨声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 稍微有点理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小凪也闭上眼睛听听看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}诶～ 呀 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好像在烤着什么的声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 回去的时候要当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 连伞都借给我太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 这把伞很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雨还是很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一班电车是几点来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 现在洗手间可以用了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有说过 要当心点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:23:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集终于柚多谷和美穂要登场了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来还真是漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 人生回顾到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们第一话没有出现过吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说起来的话我们在片头曲中有出现过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集A Channel 同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不只是同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然上级生的前辈们也会登场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:05.26,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放課後予定もなんもないし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:10.10,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨が降ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.73,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うちに集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:20.57,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君は普段から素直じゃないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.45,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日はきっと分かるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:30.58,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔がみたいだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:40.47,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな所にかくれないでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.39,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとほら近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.06,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみも友達だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:56.15,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これから何度も過ぎでいく季節も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.86,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとほら近くにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:05.87,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと一緒にいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.71,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと笑ってたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:05.26,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放课后什么预定都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:10.10,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.73,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到我家来集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:20.57,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你平时就不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.45,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天我一定会了解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:30.58,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想看到你的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:40.47,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用藏在那种地方也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.39,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.06,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:56.15,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后在更替的四季中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.86,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:05.87,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.71,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起欢笑